## Quality Standards

### **Scoring System (0-10)**

**0-3: Critical** - Barely usable, major gaps  
**4-6: Needs Work** - Functional but incomplete  
**7-8: Good** - Solid, few gaps  
**9-10: Excellent** - World-class, reference quality

### **Quality Criteria**

**Complete (0-3 points)**
- [ ] All aspects documented
- [ ] No TODOs or placeholders
- [ ] Complete coverage from basics to advanced
- [ ] All examples work and are tested

**Clear (0-2 points)**
- [ ] Written for target audience
- [ ] Concrete examples provided
- [ ] Progressive disclosure used
- [ ] Clear structure and navigation

**Correct (0-2 points)**
- [ ] Up-to-date with current practices
- [ ] Examples work as described
- [ ] Version appropriate information
- [ ] Accurate technical details

**Professional (0-2 points)**
- [ ] Polished writing and grammar
- [ ] Good formatting and presentation
- [ ] Consistent style and tone
- [ ] Professional appearance

**Discoverable (0-1 point)**
- [ ] Easy navigation and search
- [ ] Good cross-references and links
- [ ] Proper categorization and tagging
- [ ] Accessible from multiple entry points

